          <p class="font-sans text-aiq-md text-aiq-fg-secondary leading-relaxed m-0">Yes. The SQL and aptitude components are highly relevant for BI and reporting roles. The English component is particularly important for BI analysts who produce executive dashboards. Python is optional for pure BI roles &#8212; admins can scope to SQL, aptitude, and English.</p>
